{"tid":1524571,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【職員爆料】機場職員話你知點揸機場春袋！！","createTime":"2019-08-31T17:34:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T09:06:05.000Z","uid":241349,"like":69,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"d1c6034d15aa95cb483308958d2cd02d843e82e3","tid":1524571,"uid":241349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:34:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">朋友好想教各位手足有效地揸爆機場春袋！</span><br />\n但佢無連登acc，代post<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n------------------------------------------<br />\n【職員爆料】<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">813個日話取消左既航班<br />\n<strong>其實係有照飛</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只不過唔載要辦登機手續既旅客<br />\n淨係載轉機既旅客<br />\n<br />\n所以要有效塞機場除咗要塞入境大堂之外 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">仲要塞埋一號同二號檢查閘</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事關大部分既機組人員都係直接由嗰度坐巴士去架飛機度而唔洗經入境大堂<br />\n如果兩個檢查閘都塞咗過唔到先要經 <br />\n除非多人到好似812咁<br />\n機管局直接宣佈關左個空域<br />\n假如大家要有效癱瘓航班既話<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">就一定要連埋一號同二號檢查閘去塞</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">塞到既話變相機組人員被逼罷工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n奉勸大家千奇唔好塞到嗰度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係既話機場個春袋就俾人揸到渣都無得淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一號檢查閘：</span><br />\n富豪酒店落 行五分鐘到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kHz1e40.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkHz1e40.jpg&h=9792b204&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">二號檢查閘：</span><br />\n暢連路巴士站 行一分鐘到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E0eTQDj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE0eTQDj.jpg&h=7bc876db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------"},{"pid":"5ae45f0336cdea0d1c862c216b1482e4c3e59ba0","tid":1524571,"uid":123991,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:35:35.000Z","msg":"我知大家好撚嬲, 因為我地冇清算黨鐵先搞到今日咁, 但係要記得今日要去春袋報仇, 黨鐵黎緊一齊再清算！香港人加油 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lz7uo3t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLz7uo3t.jpg&h=4ed7d51c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70m9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=b6c543c6\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70m9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=dfc5166a\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\